{"tid":160220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我比某間健身中心盜用信用卡！","createTime":"2017-03-17T14:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T19:24:31.000Z","uid":66971,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"083084d0519a6eafbe2365eee46056d5393fa380","tid":160220,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日我三點幾係旺角行緊<br />\n我一路傾電話一路行<br />\n中途接左張卡<br />\n有個男人就同我講可以試玩7次<br />\n佢話成日冇人接佢野<br />\n叫我跟佢去cup個印就可以拎張試玩卡<br />\n本身諗住當幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知上到間健身中心就比人hard sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上到去 就變左第二個職員同我傾計<br />\n係咁好friendly咁問下你平日做唔做運動<br />\n係咁問左好多野<br />\n後尾佢就叫我填問卷<br />\n話填完就拎得試玩卡<br />\n我其實好想快d填完就走<br />\n中途佢有sell <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢冇提過join唔join個類既字眼<br />\n亦都冇明確咁問我參唔參加<br />\n個陣搞左好耐<br />\n佢叫我比身分證佢填資料<br />\n我以為搞份問卷啦<br />\n佢叫我比埋信用卡佢對下資料<br />\n話一兩分鐘就得<br />\n我個陣又on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  淨係想快d走就比左佢<br />\n後尾我係咁催話趕時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有講過冇咩時間join<br />\n佢就死撐話幫我問下可唔可以開個學生價比我<br />\n學生價99/week 玩三次<br />\n話做左會員先 遲d想玩再join再比錢都得<br />\n我問左佢幾次 佢話冇碌過我張卡<br />\n佢行開左去問價<br />\n<br />\n總之後尾等到佢番過黎<br />\n我話我唔join趕住要走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：職員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：如果你係冇興趣 下次話唔要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：其實我上黎淨係諗住拎張卡就走 點知你係咁sell我 冇啦啦開會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我問下manager可唔可以cancel你既申請啦<br />\n隔左一陣佢番黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：幫你cancel左架喇 不過下次冇興趣就say no la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我走左之後唔放心<br />\n打上card centre問下交易紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：card centre職員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔好意思 我怕有人盜用我張信用卡 可唔可以幫我check下今日既交易紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：今日4點10幾分有單reject左既交易 係來自......（好長唔記得左）金額係$4500 因為你張卡本身分期爆左limit 所以呢單交易reject左<br />\n我嚇撚死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我冇應承過join任何野 亦冇聽過$4500呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：呢間公司既類型係舞蹈中心健身中心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：麻煩你幫我cut左張卡佢 我冇授權呢間公司碌我張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我冇實際損失<br />\n報驚好似冇乜用<br />\n我知我好on9比左信用卡佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係想各位巴絲小心呢間野<br />\n呢間野有分店架 上年都衰過類似既野上過蘋果<br />\n間野叫：Fxx Fintness 搏x中心<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係死好彩<br />\n希望大家小心呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c170a1cff31ef00260d1339ee67f65796429c1","tid":160220,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e417f74d17d182240ffe5a80419a7ae0243aad5","tid":160220,"uid":44948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"仲以為你假膠玩野post, 原來真心到呢個年頭都仲俾人呃上健身中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你check下個腦啦係咪有事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088de58fdf4cc8da0adb2842248e9eafccf6ef5f","tid":160220,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"大把Fitness Centre出過盜用信用卡事件   你仲夠膽死拎俾佢對資料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係你打死都唔俾"},{"pid":"39116f599cb194de22b2afcfff2eac0c2fd82e0e","tid":160220,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:39:15.000Z","msg":"我知自己on9架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790b8138bef63ea42e8fa7e0e6d58a465f3d8001","tid":160220,"uid":89036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"幾多歲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097ee88fc0acef721cb93fc42e7c6fa74aef58d5","tid":160220,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"係咪新之城對面嗰間?<br />\n我之前都比佢地帶上去傾計<br />\n不過我話無eps 身上又得4百蚊 又hea答佢就放左我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11ea1155c7e61b5af1f269e864a3be8d5cd84a1","tid":160220,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:42:23.000Z","msg":"健身中心得力威信得過！"},{"pid":"4bb6cecc7aed07f1dfeabb6292145d59bbeb7871","tid":160220,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"間野係創興"},{"pid":"dffdabbeeb0f676fb68ced8b5ffbd7cdd8668ca2","tid":160220,"uid":66971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"我個陣見隔離枱都好多人比人sell緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地係咁話好快好快<br />\n諗番都覺得自己好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩本身信用卡供緊野<br />\n佢地碌唔到"},{"pid":"01f30e1c8598a7704e4dc97443692908515d5933","tid":160220,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:54:56.000Z","msg":"智障廚工購百萬課程　健身中心指事主為追求女員工 -<