你自己會有損失?"},{"pid":"dc9e87e4d751d5788665be78e618206bc9d9c4af","tid":160220,"uid":63740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n今日我三點幾係旺角行緊<br />\n我一路傾電話一路行<br />\n中途接左張卡<br />\n有個男人就同我講可以試玩7次<br />\n佢話成日冇人接佢野<br />\n叫我跟佢去cup個印就可以拎張試玩卡<br />\n本身諗住當幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知上到間健身中心就比人hard sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上到去 就變左第二個職員同我傾計<br />\n係咁好friendly咁問下你平日做唔做運動<br />\n係咁問左好多野<br />\n後尾佢就叫我填問卷<br />\n話填完就拎得試玩卡<br />\n我其實好想快d填完就走<br />\n中途佢有sell <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢冇提過join唔join個類既字眼<br />\n亦都冇明確咁問我參唔參加<br />\n個陣搞左好耐<br />\n佢叫我比身分證佢填資料<br />\n我以為搞份問卷啦<br />\n佢叫我比埋信用卡佢對下資料<br />\n話一兩分鐘就得<br />\n我個陣又on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  淨係想快d走就比左佢<br />\n後尾我係咁催話趕時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有講過冇咩時間join<br />\n佢就死撐話幫我問下可唔可以開個學生價比我<br />\n學生價99/week 玩三次<br />\n話做左會員先 遲d想玩再join再比錢都得<br />\n我問左佢幾次 佢話冇碌過我張卡<br />\n佢行開左去問價<br />\n<br />\n總之後尾等到佢番過黎<br />\n我話我唔join趕住要走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：職員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：如果你係冇興趣 下次話唔要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：其實我上黎淨係諗住拎張卡就走 點知你係咁sell我 冇啦啦開會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我問下manager可唔可以cancel你既申請啦<br />\n隔左一陣佢番黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：幫你cancel左架喇 不過下次冇興趣就say no la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我走左之後唔放心<br />\n打上card centre問下交易紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：card centre職員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔好意思 我怕有人盜用我張信用卡 可唔可以幫我check下今日既交易紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：今日4點10幾分有單reject左既交易 係來自......（好長唔記得左）金額係$4500 因為你張卡本身分期爆左limit 所以呢單交易reject左<br />\n我嚇撚死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我冇應承過join任何野 亦冇聽過$4500呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：呢間公司既類型係舞蹈中心健身中心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：麻煩你幫我cut左張卡佢 我冇授權呢間公司碌我張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我冇實際損失<br />\n報驚好似冇乜用<br />\n我知我好on9比左信用卡佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係想各位巴絲小心呢間野<br />\n呢間野有分店架 上年都衰過類似既野上過蘋果<br />\n間野叫：Fxx Fintness 搏x中心<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係死好彩<br />\n希望大家小心呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上個月都試過又係喱間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢問乜我都鳩up,<br />\n好彩冇信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d679a4bfbe0307bef22f6f073fdea9b5efc87884","tid":160220,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:05:39.000Z","msg":"成日有騙案新聞 咁你都可以中招"},{"pid":"f56169cd0ead82120adaec912ad2e8749a1fa358","tid":160220,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:06:02.000Z","msg":"胡師父真係健身界清泉<br />\n明碼實價 不硬銷"},{"pid":"6dc673a95374e806fd3bf25c5d8276f422dddfaf","tid":160220,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T1